---
import { Zap, Shield, Heart, TrendingUp, Users, Star } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="valores" class="w-full bg-white py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-4">
        Nuestros <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent" style="font-family: var(--font-secondary)">valores</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Los principios que guían cada decisión, cada campaña y cada resultado que entregamos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      
      <!-- Valor 1 -->
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-white border-2 border-purple-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <Zap className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Agilidad</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Nos movemos rápido, adaptamos estrategias al instante y ejecutamos con velocidad de tiburón.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Valor 2 -->
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white border-2 border-blue-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <Shield className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Transparencia</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Comunicación clara, reportes honestos y cero promesas vacías. Solo resultados reales.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Valor 3 -->
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-white border-2 border-green-200 hover:border-green-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-green-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <Heart className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Pasión</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Cada proyecto es una oportunidad de demostrar nuestra obsesión por la excelencia.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Valor 4 -->
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-white border-2 border-purple-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <TrendingUp className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Resultados</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          No nos conformamos con el esfuerzo. Medimos, optimizamos y entregamos ROI real.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Valor 5 -->
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white border-2 border-blue-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <Users className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Colaboración</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Trabajamos codo a codo con nuestros clientes. Tu éxito es nuestro éxito.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Valor 6 -->
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-white border-2 border-green-200 hover:border-green-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-green-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <Star className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Excelencia</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Cada detalle importa. Cada campaña es una obra maestra. Sin excepciones.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

